title: Episode 206: Y'all Think This Is Funny? (Feat. Ann Marie)
itunes:title: Episode 206: Y'all Think This Is Funny? (Feat. Ann Marie)
description:
R&B artist Ann Marie joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and speaks on how growing up in Chicago has shaped her as a woman, why sex isnt' so exciting to her, her issues with trust and abandonment, and much more. Gigi even takes Ann Marie to school regarding internal and external orgasms...enjoy!
